PLACEHOLDER — replace this file with your actual prompt.

To use:
1. Convert your 40-page DOCX prompt to plain text (UTF-8).
2. Save it as: backend/prompts/privacy-policy-auditor-full.txt
3. Upload via Render → Files → Secret Files (path: /app/prompts/privacy-policy-auditor-full.txt)
   OR commit directly to the repo if the content is not sensitive.

The file is loaded by: backend/src/integrations/claude-api.js → loadPrivacyPolicyPrompt()
It is used as the system prompt (with prompt caching) for analyzePrivacyPolicy().

Expected output format from Claude:
{
  "criteria": [
    { "id": 1, "score": 4, "explanation": "..." },
    ...37 total items...
  ],
  "total_score": 120,
  "max_score": 185,
  "percentage": 64.9,
  "category": "MODERATE"
}
